17 year old British model & miss England finalist. \n\nRheanna Cartier grew up in England in small countryside town. When she was 14 years old she relocated to Denmark due to bullying. She spent a school year there & returned to England. She is now a fashion model & an anti bullying ambassador. She is also a Miss England finalist & the finals will be held this summer.
